OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,FCameras which can detect drivers who
OL,7,Fuse mobile phones behind the wheel or
OL,8,Fwho do not wear a seatbelt are being
OL,9,Fdeployed in Scotland for the first
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FIn the largest survey of its kind ever
OL,13,Fundertaken in the UK, the cameras will
OL,14,Fmonitor behaviour at 12 sites in
OL,15,FScotland for the next six months.
OL,17,FThe data will be used to inform
OL,18,Fenforcement strategies in the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,FTransport Scotland says that among
OL,7,FScotland's estimated 4.7 million daily
OL,8,Fvehicle journeys, it is estimated
OL,9,Faround 169,000 drivers do not use
OL,10,Fseatbelts.
OL,12,FMore than 28,000 may use handheld
OL,13,Fdevices every day behind the wheel.
OL,15,FThe survey will see two cameras
OL,16,Fmounted on trailers and they will use
OL,17,FAI processing techniques to determine
OL,18,Fthe probability of an offence.
OL,20,FThey will rotate around locations in
OL,21,FScotland over the six months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,FTwo stages of human review will
OL,7,Fvalidate the cameras' findings.
OL,9,FThere is currently no timetable for
OL,10,Fenforcement in relation to the survey,
OL,11,FTransport Scotland said.
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Fiona Hyslop said:
OL,14,F"We know using a mobile phone behind
OL,15,Fthe wheel when driving and not wearing
OL,16,Fa seatbelt are two of the highest
OL,17,Ffactors which risk death or injury on
OL,18,Four roads and present significant
OL,19,Fdangers to other drivers and
OL,20,Fpassengers on Scotland's roads.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,F"This trial will give us the most
OL,7,Fcomprehensive picture yet of the scale
OL,8,Fof these issues.
OL,10,F"Recent statistics show that almost a
OL,11,Fquarter of in-car fatalities were of
OL,12,Fdrivers and passengers who were not
OL,13,Fwearing a seatbelt at the time, and
OL,14,Ftens of thousands of drivers continue
OL,15,Fto use mobile phones behind the wheel
OL,16,Fon a daily basis at serious risk and
OL,17,Fdanger to themselves and others.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,F"We cannot allow that to continue, and
OL,7,Fthis trial will help inform the next
OL,8,Fsteps in tackling these behaviours
OL,9,Fthrough enforcement, education and
OL,10,Ftargeted investment.
OL,12,F"The Scottish Government remains
OL,13,Fabsolutely committed to our goal of
OL,14,Fmaking Scotland's roads the safest in
OL,15,Fthe world by 2030. The use of new
OL,16,Ftechnology to tackle some of the most
OL,17,Fdangerous driver behaviour will help
OL,18,Fus achieve that goal."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
