OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773209293
OL,3,CCameras which can detect drivers using
OL,4,Cmobile phones coming to Scottish roads
OL,6,FGeoff Collins of Acusensus, the
OL,7,Fcompany behind the camera technology,
OL,8,Fsaid: "As the UK's largest ever survey
OL,9,Fof mobile phone and seatbelt use, this
OL,10,Fproject will provide clear evidence
OL,11,Ffor the scale of poor driving
OL,12,Fbehaviours on Scottish roads.
OL,14,F"We know from existing operational
OL,15,Fschemes that this knowledge gives us a
OL,16,Fchance to change bad habits, which
OL,17,Fwill result in fewer avoidable
OL,18,Fcollisions and casualties."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
